# Product Requirements Document (PRD)
## Product Name
Medini Intelligence

## Overview
Medini Intelligence is an AI-powered web application that generates structured knowledge and technical content using a Large Language Model (LLM).

## Problem Statement
Users require a controllable, structured AI assistant for technical documentation and knowledge generation instead of generic chatbot outputs.

## Target Users
- AI learners
- Technical writers
- Product managers
- Developers
- Content creators

## Core Features
- Chat-based AI interface
- Adjustable system instructions
- Parameter controls (temperature, top_p, max_tokens)
- Streaming responses
- OAuth-based authentication
- Web deployment

## Success Metrics
- Initial token latency < 3 seconds
- Structured output consistency
- User engagement rate
- Token efficiency

## Roadmap
- Persistent memory
- Tool calling integration
- Agentic workflows
- API version release
